# 🚀 Radijator QR — Deploy Guide

Ovaj dokument služi kao podsetnik za deploy i rad na produkcionom serveru.

Server:
- IP: 91.92.118.237
- Path: /var/www/radijator-qr

---

# 🔐 1. Prijava na server

```bash
ssh ubuntu@91.92.118.237
cd /var/www/radijator-qr
```

---

# 📦 2. Standardni deploy (BEZ migracija)

```bash
git pull origin main
composer install --no-dev --optimize-autoloader
php artisan optimize:clear
npm run build
sudo systemctl restart php8.3-fpm
sudo systemctl reload nginx
```

---

# 🧱 3. Deploy SA migracijama

```bash
git pull origin main
composer install --no-dev --optimize-autoloader
php artisan optimize:clear
php artisan migrate --force
npm run build
sudo systemctl restart php8.3-fpm
sudo systemctl reload nginx
```

---

# ⚠️ VAŽNO — MIGRACIJE

## Bezbedno:
```bash
php artisan migrate --force
```

## OPASNO (BRIŠE PODATKE):
```bash
php artisan migrate:fresh --force
php artisan migrate:fresh --seed --force
php artisan db:seed --force
```

---

# 🔄 4. Refresh aplikacije

```bash
php artisan optimize:clear
npm run build
sudo systemctl restart php8.3-fpm
sudo systemctl reload nginx
```

---

# 🧪 5. Provera baze

```bash
php artisan tinker
```

---

# 🔧 6. Ako frontend ne radi

```bash
npm install
npm run build
```

